      skos:note "Feedback/Help tool above the line for MVP. MCP tool that sends user confirmation (phone or email) and forwards request text to Scarlet. Front stays active only for this. Primary churn-prevention mechanism — response within minutes from Scarlet personally." .

    narr:Claim_TeamPlanAtLaunch a narr:Claim ;
